    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with documented justification. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Validation evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
